38 required for an employee by subsection 3 from that employee's wages and shall remit
39 100% of the combined premium contribution required by subsection 3 to the fund. The
40 employee shall pay 50% of the premium amount as required by subsection 3, unless
41 the employer chooses to deduct up to 50% of the premium required for an employee
42 by subsection 3 from that employee's wages.
