18 Sec. 11. 26 MRSA §850-F, sub-§11 is enacted to read:
19 11. Enforcement to collect delinquent premium contributions, penalties and
20 assessments. If an employer fails to make a payment in whole or in part of premium
21 contributions, including penalties or assessments imposed, and the employer has exhausted
